content.text: Let me tell you about myself. My name is Alex Chen. I'm a software engineer at TechCorp. I'm 6 feet tall and weigh 185 pounds. I drive a 2024 Tesla Model 3. I live in Austin, Texas with my dog Max, a golden retriever. I went to UT Austin for computer science.

Nice to meet you, Alex! I've noted all of that. You're a software engineer at TechCorp, living in Austin with Max your golden retriever. UT Austin CS grad, driving a 2024 Tesla Model 3. Got it all down.
My birthday is June 15, 1990. I'm on a keto diet and I go to the gym every morning at 6am. My favorite programming language is Rust but I mostly write TypeScript at work.
Got it - born June 15 1990, keto diet, gym at 6am daily. Rust fan but TypeScript professionally at TechCorp. Solid routine.
